## 🔧 Hardware Design (Altium)

The ArchEV system includes a custom-designed PCB developed using Altium Designer.

### 📸 PCB Design
hardware/images/archev_pcb_3d.png

### 📄 Complete Hardware Design
Includes schematic, PCB layout, and BOM:
hardware/schematics/archev_hardware_design.pdf

### ⚡ Key Features
- Teensy 4.1 microcontroller integration  
- Motor driver interfaces (PUL/DIR)  
- Stable power input with filtering  
- Modular connectors for scalability  
